            . I keep a lodging house in <placeName id="t18080217-84-crimeloc491">Whitechapel</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18080217-84-crimeloc491" type="placeName" value="Whitechapel"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18080217-84-crimeloc491" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080217-84-off489 t18080217-84-crimeloc491"></join>.</p>
               <p>Q. Did the prisoner come to lodge with you. - A. Yes, on the 28th of last month he came for one night only, and he agreed and paid me for one night.</p>
               <p>Q. Did any body lodge in the same room. - A. Yes, there was another man in a bed in the same room. On the next morning, from information of my girl. I searched the prisoner; I found upon him a pair of sheets, one round his waist and the other in his small clothes, they are my sheets, there are my marks on them, R F.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18080217-84-verdict492" type="verdictDescription">
